Rapper, dance-hall and afro-fusion artiste Ghetto P has adopted the new stage name of Khalil. This is coming just as he released a new single titled: Cold Blanket. Often compared to Mike Tyson’s left-right hit combos for his ability to switch styles, the artiste whose real name is Khalil Hassan has rebranded as Khalil, which means ‘friend’ in Arabic. Currently signed to a record deal with a new label, Kronik Records, Khalil is set to release an EP titled Grown 